title: Neil Young 1994-10-02 Bridge School Benefit
description:
Here is a nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Neil Young & Crazy Horse (acoustic with keyboards and drums)
Bridge School Benefit
October 2, 1994
Shoreline Amphitheatre
Mountain View, California, USA

solo:
00:00:00 All Along The Watchtower
00:04:02 The Needle And The Damage Done
00:06:07 outro

with Crazy Horse:
00:06:24 My Heart
00:09:55 Prime Of Life
00:15:15 Driveby
00:20:18 Sleeps With Angels
00:23:59 Hey Hey My My (Into The Black)
00:29:27 Train Of Love
00:34:11 Change Your Mind
00:53:52 Neil talk

00:54:59 Piece Of Crap 
00:59:53 final outro
01:00:08 end

Lineage: 2nd gen. pre-broadcast SVHS tape > Sony WV-DR7 > Sony DVMC-DA2 Media Converter > Apple Macintosh Final Cut Pro (minor "nip and tuck" edits, filter to replace bottom of screen "head switch jitter" with black and chaptering) > Compressor > DVD Studio Pro (menu and authoring) > VIDEO_TS file set.

Primary audio source: audio CD's received in trade > Pro Tools (synch with VHS tape audio and add splices from that source, normalization, clicks removed manually). Audio placed back into Final Cut Pro before Compressor down-sampling. 

Video: NTSC 720x480 VBR 7.7 Mbps peak, 6.2 Mbps average data rate, 2-pass.
Audio: choice of AC3/Dolby Digital 2/0 (L,R), 48 kHz sample rate, 448 kbps data rate 
or
Linear PCM 2 channel 48kHz 16 bit (monophonic audio). 
Enjoy and SHARE!
